description.fr_FR: ical2Calendar permet d'importer un calendrier ical dans le plugin agenda officiel que celui-ci viennent de Google, Outlook, Nextcloud ou autre.
description.en_US: ical2Calendar lets you import an ical calendar into the official calendar plugin, whether it's from Google, Outlook, Nextcloud or another source.
description.es_ES: ical2Calendar le permite importar un calendario ical en el plugin de calendario oficial, ya venga de Google, Outlook, Nextcloud u otra fuente.
description.de_DE: mit ical2Calendar können Sie einen ical-Kalender in das offizielle Kalender-Plugin importieren, unabhängig davon, ob dieser von Google, Outlook, Nextcloud oder anderen Anbietern stammt.
description.it_IT: ical2Calendar consente di importare un calendario ical nel plugin calendario ufficiale, sia che provenga da Google, Outlook, Nextcloud o altra fonte.
description.pt_PT: o ical2Calendar permite-lhe importar um calendário ical para o plug-in de calendário oficial, quer seja proveniente do Google, Outlook, Nextcloud ou outra fonte.
